{"title":"报告","authors":["田汉"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"报告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我们又投入了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的怀抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，我们又看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松花江上的帆樯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们离了你们，同胞们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过五十来天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却进展得如此的辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也给世界的战争贩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个迎头的痛击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但全靠着毛主席的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明的领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和诸位同胞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力增加生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援胜利的前方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是要去巴黎吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但法国的反动政府"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在美帝的指使下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不给签入境的护照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来许派八位去参加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说只要答应给北平的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法国领事馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去一个电报。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们坚持无条件的原则"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不上帝国主义的鬼圈套。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决定一个也不去法国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布拉哈的各国阵容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经够整齐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"联合以苏联为首的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十六国的人民代表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在捷克的国会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断然竖起了战旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥护民主和平的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不需要任何护照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传达到每一个人民的心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个分不开的大会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是在布拉哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或是在巴黎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在布拉哈会场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可以听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居里的讲演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在巴黎会场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照样有郭沫若的怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这两处的声音溶成一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新战争挑拨者发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柏林问题不是已经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始解决了吗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这一趟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算没有白走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有百年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝斗争的经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们击败了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本帝国主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和美蒋反动集团的匪兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚定沉毅的发言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增加了人民民主国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的信心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和苏联的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟般的合作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证了世界的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持久和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，同胞们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们不能想象；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“南京解放”的消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样轰动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个大会的会场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们抱着你猛烈接吻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们把鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔在你头上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们欢喜得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出眼泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象他们自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们半夜里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围在我们的旅馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾那卡尔巴阡山吹来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么冷的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几千个捷克的青年男女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高喊着“乌拉！毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东，毛泽东！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又喊着“新中国万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国人民万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那声音震撼着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东欧的夜空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对中国人民的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们真是这样的关心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位法属非洲的代表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几次提到毛主席的英名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说“毛主席不仅是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民的领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也和斯大林先生一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是全世界被压迫者的救星！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从布拉哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们回到了莫斯科。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加了检阅世界劳动人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗力量的五一节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参观了图书馆，博物馆………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也欣尝了画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧了戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听了歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们象入了革命的宝山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的收获。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那样的多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同胞们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是胜利了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们还得努力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取全中国人民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迅速解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要学习苏联的榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛主席领导下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变农业中国为工业中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使中国真正的自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独立，富强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远东的和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能得到保障，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能得到保障！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年五月十四日。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}